ontribution 401(k) retirement plan, which is subject to the provisions of the", "bbox": [194.9, 1050.2, 1103.7, 1071.1]}, {"text": "Employee Retirement Income Security Act of 1974. We also sponsor a deferred profit sharing plan for the", "bbox": [153.2, 1075.2, 1103.7, 1096.1]}, {"text": "benefit of the full-time employees of our Canadian subsidiaries. Under these plans, we match a percentage of the", "bbox": [153.2, 1100.2, 1103.7, 1121.1]}, {"text": "participants’ contributions up to a specified amount. Company contributions to the plans were $23, $22 and $19", "bbox": [153.2, 1125.2, 1103.8, 1146.1]}, {"text": "in the years ended December 31, 2016, 2015 and 2014, respectively.", "bbox": [153.2, 1150.3, 724.4, 1171.1]}, {"text": "Environmental Matters", "bbox": [153.2, 1212.6, 363.5, 1233.4]}, {"text": "The Company and its operations are subject to various laws and related regulations governing", "bbox": [194.9, 1250.3, 1103.7, 1271.1]}, {"text": "environmental matters. Under such laws, an owner or lessee of real estate may be liable for the costs of removal", "bbox": [153.2, 1275.3, 1103.6, 1296.2]}, {"text": "or remediation of certain hazardous or toxic substances located on or in, or emanating from, such property, as", "bbox": [153.2, 1300.3, 1103.8, 1321.2]}, {"text": "well as investigation of property damage. We incur ongoing expenses associated with the performance of", "bbox": [153.2, 1325.3, 1103.7, 1346.2]}, {"text": "appropriate remediation at certain locations.", "bbox": [153.2, 1350.3, 521.6, 1371.2]}, {"text": "82", "bbox": [618.1, 1475.4, 638.9, 1496.2]}]}